{"tid":1938224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「準備大爆發」食衛局真係好撚兒戲 香港人自求多福","createTime":"2020-03-22T11:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T15:14:22.000Z","uid":114360,"like":371,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"97d956f680b84ad3614685abb606edf005b5e6ff","tid":1938224,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:42:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第一宗罪： 醫管局對調陰性陽性樣本，確診人士周街走</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n醫管局瑪麗醫院化驗室昨日測試7個來自亞洲國際博覽館檢測中心的樣本，當中4個樣本在化驗過程中被對調，其中2名樣本屬陽性的人更分別回到家中和酒店。醫管局和衞生署下午開記者會，醫管局總行政經理庾慧玲表示，每個化驗樣本都有標示號碼，今次出錯涉及對調號碼，指因為化驗過程和步驟欠嚴謹所致。<br />\n<br />\nSource： <a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071753&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=32ee84ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071753&h=8f3432b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071753</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>第二宗罪：衛生署不派任何手帶給予回港人士以及了解隔離事宜，非常兒戲</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】抵港前14日，在外地逗留的人都必須強制檢疫，但有在美國經台灣，轉機到香港的學生表示入境時職員無要求隔離或戴電子手帶。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=21112&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl.hkott.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D21112%26ct%3D1&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=9d609b8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=21112&amp;ct=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第三宗罪：家居檢疫手帶漏洞百出冇撚用，只靠港人自律</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n政府上周四（19日）起在機場向所有外地入境者派電子手帶作家居檢疫，連日出現不少甩漏，至昨日仍有人未能啟動手帶；而前日網上流傳有人以不同形式脫下手帶，或戴手帶外出，顯示措施效果成疑。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20200322/s00001/1584815361162/家居檢疫多甩漏-網傳剪手帶避監察-違檢疫令不警告即檢控-昨截4人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200322%2Fs00001%2F1584815361162%2F%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E5%A4%9A%E7%94%A9%E6%BC%8F-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%89%AA%E6%89%8B%E5%B8%B6%E9%81%BF%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F-%E9%81%95%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E4%BB%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%8D%B3%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-%E6%98%A8%E6%88%AA4%E4%BA%BA&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=f3a28611\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200322%2Fs00001%2F1584815361162%2F%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E5%A4%9A%E7%94%A9%E6%BC%8F-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%89%AA%E6%89%8B%E5%B8%B6%E9%81%BF%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F-%E9%81%95%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E4%BB%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%8D%B3%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-%E6%98%A8%E6%88%AA4%E4%BA%BA&h=24856ef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20200322/s00001/1584815361162/家居檢疫多甩漏-網傳剪手帶避監察-違檢疫令不警告即檢控-昨截4人</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母港共政府，係唔係想殺死香港人先甘心！<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b61b4226fa8cf006c1b585a63427e6afd6d70fdd","tid":1938224,"uid":18597,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"係唔係想殺死香港人先甘心&lt;- 香港政府表示：係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98512fed4bdd1a14fdd884eade79462f2107c777","tid":1938224,"uid":114360,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYg8qh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYg8qh6.jpg&h=08870223&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOak0Rs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOak0Rs.jpg&h=c6003ccd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"314c963b